quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  29,64,WE MA HEDHIHIL-HEJÆTU ED-DUNJA ‘ILLA LEHWUN WE LA’IBUN WE ‘INNE ED-DAREL-’AHIRETE LEHIJEL-HEJEWANU LEW KANU JA’LEMUNE
  29,65,FE’IDHA REKIBU FIL-FULKI DE’AW ELLAHE MUHLISINE LEHU ED-DINE FELEMMA NEXHXHAHUM ‘ILAL-BERRI ‘IDHA HUM JUSHRIKUNE
  29,66,LIJEKFURU BIMA ‘ATEJNAHUM WE LIJETEMETTA’U FESEWFE JA’LEMUNE
  29,67,‘EWELEM JEREW ‘ENNA XHE’ALNA HEREMÆN ‘AMINÆN WE JUTEHATTEFU EN-NASU MIN HEWLIHIM ‘EFEBIALBATILI JU’UMINUNE WE BINI’METI ELLAHI JEKFURUNE
  29,68,WE MEN ‘EDHLEMU MIMMENI EFTERA ‘ALA ELLAHI KEDHIBÆN ‘EW KEDHDHEBE BIL-HEKKI LEMMA XHA’EHU ‘ELEJSE FI XHEHENNEME METHWEN LILKAFIRINE
  29,69,WEL-LEDHINE XHAHEDU FINA LENEHDIJENNEHUM SUBULENA WE ‘INNALL-LLAHE LEME’AL-MUHSININE